2011-09-19T04:38:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/sri-lanka-has-policy-space-if-inflation-climbs-cabraal-says.html
Sri Lanka  has “monetary policy
space’’ to take measures if inflation accelerates, central bank
Governor Nivard Cabraal said in  Colombo  today.  He didn’t elaborate.  To contact the reporter on this story:
